---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import LegacyHeader from '../components/LegacyHeader.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import ContactSection from '../components/ContactSection.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import ButtonPrimary from '../components/ButtonPrimary.astro';
import ButtonSecondary from '../components/ButtonSecondary.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Technical SEO Services In The Philippines - Bright Forge SEO" description="Fix crawling issues, speed up your site, and boost rankings. Our tech SEO services in the Philippines make your site easier to find and faster to trust.">
  <LegacyHeader slot="header" />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Hero
    badgeIcon="fas fa-cogs"
    badgeText="Technical SEO Experts"
    title="Technical SEO Services In The Philippines"
    breadcrumbCurrent="Technical SEO Services Philippines"
  >
    <Fragment slot="story">
      <p>Have you ever wondered why your website isn't performing as well as it should, despite having great content and beautiful design? I've seen it countless times—business owners investing heavily in their online presence only to be held back by invisible technical barriers. One client came to us after spending months creating premium content that simply wasn't ranking. The culprit? Technical SEO issues that were hiding their site from Google's view.</p>
      <p>At Bright Forge SEO, we specialize in uncovering and fixing these hidden obstacles. Our technical SEO services go beyond surface-level optimizations to address the foundational elements that search engines care about most. We transform your website into a well-oiled machine that both search engines and users love to interact with—because when your technical foundation is solid, everything else falls into place.</p>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="actions">
      <ButtonPrimary href="/contact" text="Fix Your Technical Foundation" />
      <ButtonSecondary href="#services" text="View Our Services" />
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="visual">
      <div class="hero-image-container">
        <div class="technical-icon-grid">
          <div class="tech-icon"><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i></div>
          <div class="tech-icon"><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i></div>
          <div class="tech-icon"><i class="fas fa-sitemap"></i></div>
          <div class="tech-icon"><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i></div>
          <div class="tech-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i></div>
          <div class="tech-icon"><i class="fas fa-code"></i></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <!-- Why Technical SEO Section -->
  <section class="why-technical-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Technical SEO Is Your Website's <span>Secret Weapon</span></h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content-explanation">
        <div class="content-card">
          <div class="content-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="content-text">
            <p>Technical SEO is like the engine of your car—you don't see it, but it powers everything. While content and backlinks get most of the attention, technical issues can completely undermine your SEO efforts if left unaddressed. Search engines need to efficiently crawl, render, and index your website before your content even has a chance to rank.</p>
            
            <p>Our technical SEO services ensure your website meets and exceeds Google's increasingly demanding technical requirements, giving you a competitive edge in the Philippine market where many businesses still overlook these critical optimizations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Technical SEO Services Section -->
  <section id="services" class="services-section-new">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="services-layout">
        <div class="services-content">
          <h2>Our Core Technical SEO <span>Services</span></h2>

          <div class="service-list">
            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Site Architecture Optimization</h3>
              <p>Streamline your URL structure, internal linking, site hierarchy, XML sitemaps, and robots.txt to help search engines crawl and understand your site efficiently.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Performance Optimization</h3>
              <p>Improve page speed, Core Web Vitals, server response times, and resource delivery through minification, compression, and image optimization for better rankings and user experience.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Mobile Optimization</h3>
              <p>Ensure mobile-first indexing compliance with responsive design, mobile usability fixes, proper touch element spacing, and lightning-fast mobile page speeds.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Security & Indexing</h3>
              <p>Implement SSL, manage HTTPS migrations, configure security headers, and optimize crawl budgets to improve index coverage and protect your site's reputation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="services-visual">
          <div class="visual-card">
            <div class="visual-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Technical Excellence</h3>
            <p class="visual-stat">98%</p>
            <p class="visual-label">Technical Score Improvement</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Process Section -->
  <section class="process-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="process-header">
        <h2>Our Technical SEO <span>Process</span></h2>
        <p>We follow a systematic approach to identify, fix, and monitor your website's technical health.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-grid">
        <div class="process-box orange-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Technical Audit</h3>
          <p>We perform a comprehensive technical analysis of your website using advanced tools to identify all issues affecting your search performance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box white-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Issue Prioritization</h3>
          <p>We categorize and prioritize technical issues based on their impact on your search rankings and user experience.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box orange-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Implementation Plan</h3>
          <p>We create a detailed roadmap for fixing technical issues, ensuring changes are made safely and effectively.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box white-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Optimization Execution</h3>
          <p>Our team implements the necessary technical fixes and optimizations, carefully monitoring for any potential impacts.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box orange-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-vial"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Testing & Validation</h3>
          <p>We thoroughly test all changes across different devices and browsers to ensure everything works perfectly.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box white-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Monitoring & Maintenance</h3>
          <p>We continuously monitor your website's technical health and performance, addressing new issues as they arise.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="benefits-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="benefits-header">
        <h2>The Benefits of Strong <span>Technical SEO</span></h2>
        <p>Investing in technical SEO delivers lasting advantages for your website and business.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="benefits-layout">
        <div class="benefits-visual">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551434678-e076c223a692?w=800&q=80"
            alt="Professional team collaborating on technical SEO projects"
            class="benefits-image"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="benefits-grid">
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Improved Rankings</h3>
            <p>A technically optimized website has a better chance of ranking higher in search results, as search engines can easily crawl and understand your content.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Faster Loading Times</h3>
            <p>Technical optimizations lead to faster page loading times, reducing bounce rates and improving user engagement.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Better User Experience</h3>
            <p>A well-structured, fast-loading website provides a superior user experience, leading to higher conversion rates.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Mobile Excellence</h3>
            <p>Your website will perform flawlessly across all devices, capturing the growing mobile audience in the Philippines.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <ContactSection />

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</MainLayout>

<style>
/* Technical Icon Grid (used in Hero visual slot) */
.hero-image-container {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 500px;
}

.technical-icon-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 2rem;
  padding: 2rem;
}

.tech-icon {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: 20px;
  color: white;
  font-size: 2rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes float {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
}

.tech-icon:nth-child(odd) {
  animation-delay: 1s;
}

.tech-icon:nth-child(even) {
  animation-delay: 2s;
}

.tech-icon:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.05);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
  border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .technical-icon-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .technical-icon-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .tech-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
}

/* NEW Services Section - Reference Image Style */
.services-section-new {
  padding: 5rem 0;
  background: white;
}

.services-layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: start;
}

.services-content h2 {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.services-content h2 span {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
}

.service-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.service-item {
  background: #f8f9fa;
  border-left: 4px solid #f97316;
  padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.service-item:hover {
  background: #f0f1f3;
  transform: translateX(5px);
}

.service-item h3 {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.service-item p {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: #666;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
}

.services-visual {
  position: sticky;
  top: 2rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  min-height: 400px;
}

.visual-card {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.05), rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.05));
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 3rem 2rem;
  text-align: center;
  border: 1px solid rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.2);
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.visual-icon {
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
  color: white;
  font-size: 2rem;
}

.visual-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.visual-stat {
  font-size: 4rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
  line-height: 1;
}

.visual-label {
  color: #666;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .services-layout {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .services-visual {
    position: static;
  }
}

/* Process Section */
.process-section {
  padding: 5rem 0;
  background: #f8f9fa;
}

.process-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.process-header h2 {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.process-header h2 span {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
}

.process-header p {
  color: #666;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.process-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 0;
}

.process-box {
  padding: 3rem 2rem;
  text-align: center;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.process-box:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  z-index: 10;
}

.process-box.orange-bg {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
}

.process-box.orange-bg h3,
.process-box.orange-bg p {
  color: white;
}

.process-box.white-bg {
  background: white;
}

.process-box.white-bg h3 {
  color: #1a1a1a;
}

.process-box.white-bg p {
  color: #666;
}

.process-box-icon {
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.process-box.orange-bg .process-box-icon {
  color: white;
}

.process-box.white-bg .process-box-icon {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
}

.process-box:hover .process-box-icon {
  transform: scale(1.1);
}

.process-box h3 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.process-box p {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .process-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .process-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}

/* Benefits Section */
.benefits-section {
  padding: 5rem 0;
  background: white;
}

.benefits-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.benefits-header h2 {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.benefits-header h2 span {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
}

.benefits-header p {
  color: #666;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.benefits-layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: center;
}

.benefits-visual {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.benefits-image {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 400px;
  height: 500px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 20px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

.benefits-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 2rem;
}

.benefit-card {
  background: white;
  border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  text-align: center;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.benefit-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.benefit-icon {
  width: 70px;
  height: 70px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #FF6B35);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
  color: white;
  font-size: 1.75rem;
}

.benefit-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.benefit-card p {
  color: #666;
  line-height: 1.6;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .benefits-layout {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .benefits-image {
    height: 400px;
    max-width: 100%;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .benefits-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}
</style>

